","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"YouBike 增設站點："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 李宗豪積極爭取在 A7 重劃區增設 YouBike 站點，目前已完成會勘並確定增設的站點包括：下湖營區、大湖紀念公園、文青國中小、郵政公園、郵政物流園區、嶺頂站、牛角坡路等。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"14-16"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 其中下湖營區、大湖紀念公園已派工施作，文青國中小預計今年 6 月點交土地後即可施作，郵政公園及郵政物流園區尚在中華郵政流程中，嶺頂站及牛角坡路則在規劃設計階段。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"16"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自行車道規劃："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 李宗豪建議規劃自行車道以提升騎車安全。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"13"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"二、教育方面："}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文青國中小工程："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 幼兒園已於 2023 年 6 月完工，國中小也於 2023 年 12 月完工，並如期招生。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"17"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 李宗豪持續追蹤二期工程和活動中心的進度，並要求市府加速發包開工。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"18"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文青國中小周邊交通改善："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 李宗豪爭取在文青國中小設置 YouBike 站點和公車站及候車亭。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"13, 15"}]},{"type":"text","value":" YouBike 站點預計配合活動中心完工後一起開放。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"15"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"ty