"props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大埔垃圾轉運站退場："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 李宗豪強力要求大埔垃圾轉運站退場，並已爭取到市長承諾於 2024 年底退場。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"25-28"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 目前環保局規劃另覓新址，改為室內倉儲密閉作業，預計今年 11 月發包動工，明年 3 月完工。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"29"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 李宗豪持續追蹤進度，並要求環保局提出具體的退場計畫和時程，包括增加垃圾車、清潔隊員等措施，以達成垃圾直送不轉運的目標。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"30"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"四、公共設施方面："}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 滯洪池公園："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 公滯 1 濕轉乾改建公園計畫預計於 2024 年 7 月開工。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"31, 32"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 李宗豪建議多挑選幾個滯洪池評估改建為公園，同時兼顧防災及休憩功能。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"33"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大坪頂公園："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 公九用地取得已召開第一次公聽會，預計開發進度將比文高三公園快，未來有機會成為大型公園。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"31"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文德公園步道改善："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 文德公園行人步道已於 2024 年開始整修，目前已接近完工。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"34"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"郵政公園改善："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 李宗豪爭取改善郵政公園設施，包括擴展遊樂場、增設遊具等，郵政公司已將建議帶回研議。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"35, 36"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"龜山國民運動中心："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 龜山國民運動中心已於 2024 年 6 月成功決標，預計下半年開工。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"37"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 李宗豪也建議在運動中心內規劃幼兒體適能空間。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"38"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人行道破損問題："}]},{"type":"text","value":" 李宗豪持續關注人行道破損問題，並成功推動修法，未來建商若因施工導致公共設施損毀，必須立即修復，否則建案將被勒令停工。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"39, 40"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李宗豪在 A7 重劃區積極推動各項建設，並持續追蹤進度，以改善居民生活品質，提升區域發展。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"李宗豪對-a7-重劃區的社區服務匯總","depth":2,"text":"李宗豪對 A7 重劃區的社區服務匯總"},{"id":"李宗豪議員-a7-重劃區交通規劃和建設現況","depth":2,"text":"李宗豪議員 A7 重劃區交通規劃和建設現況"},{"id":"a7-重劃區的問題與李宗豪議員的處理方式","depth":2,"text":"A7 重劃區的問題與李宗豪議員的處理方式"},{"id":"李宗豪-a7-重劃區推動的建設項目及進度","depth":2,"text":"李宗豪 A7 重劃區推動的建設項目及進度"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s2000.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s2000.md","_extension":"md"}